{"type":"message","id":"80e68847","parentId":"2d2db2c2","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:55:57.212Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Chat messages since your last reply - for context]\nAssistant: 👋 Hi! I'm the Builderz assistant.\nAsk me anything about our blockchain development services, projects, or\n  how we can help bring your Web3 ideas to life!\nUser: hi there\nAssistant: <p>Hey there! 👋<br>Great to have you here — how can I help today with Builderz?</p>\nUser: tell me somthing in summery about builderz\nAssistant: <p>Sure! Here’s a quick summary of <strong>Builderz</strong>:</p>\n<p><strong>Builderz</strong> is a blockchain-focused development team that helps turn Web3 ideas into real products.<br>They typically support things like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smart contract development</strong></li>\n<li><strong>DApp (decentralized app) building</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Blockchain consulting and architecture</strong></li>\n<li><strong>End-to-end Web3 product development</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>In short: if someone has a Web3 concept, Builderz helps design, build, and launch it. 🚀</p>\n<p>If you want, I can also give you a <strong>one-line pitch</strong>, a <strong>detailed version</strong>, or a <strong>client-friendly intro message</strong> you can reuse.</p>\nUser: tell me names of your services\nAssistant: <p>Absolutely — here are our core services at Builderz:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smart Contract Development</strong></li>\n<li><strong>DApp Development</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Blockchain Consulting &amp; Architecture</strong></li>\n<li><strong>End-to-End Web3 Product Development</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Smart Contract Audits &amp; Security Review</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Web3 Integration (Wallets, APIs, On-chain features)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Maintenance &amp; Scaling Support</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want, I can also break these into <strong>technical services</strong> vs <strong>business-friendly packages</strong>.</p>\nUser: BTW how are you?\nAssistant: <p>I’m doing great, thanks for asking 😄<br>Always happy to chat — and even happier when it’s about building cool Web3 stuff.</p>\n<p>How are <em>you</em> doing today?</p>\nUser: i am doing good\nAssistant: <p>Love to hear that 🙌<br>If you want, we can keep going — I can show you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>a <strong>simple pricing/package style breakdown</strong></li>\n<li>a <strong>client-ready intro message</strong> for Builderz</li>\n<li>or a <strong>step-by-step plan</strong> to start your Web3 project</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Your call 🚀</p>\nUser: list name of all major services of builderz\nAssistant: <p>Absolutely — here are the <strong>major Builderz services</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Smart Contract Development</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>DApp Development</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>Blockchain Consulting &amp; Architecture</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>End-to-End Web3 Product Development</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>Smart Contract Audits &amp; Security Review</strong>  </li>\n<li><strong>Web3 Integrations</strong> (wallets, APIs, on-chain features)  </li>\n<li><strong>Maintenance &amp; Scaling Support</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>If you want, I can also group these into <strong>startup packages</strong> (MVP, Growth, Enterprise).</p>\nUser: okay give me summery of your term of services\nAssistant: <p>Sure — here’s a <strong>simple summary of our Terms of Service</strong> (plain-language version):</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p><strong>Scope of work</strong><br>We define deliverables, timeline, and tech stack before starting.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Client responsibilities</strong><br>You provide required assets, feedback, approvals, and access on time.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Payments</strong><br>Projects are usually milestone-based (or retainer). Late payments may pause work.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Revisions &amp; change requests</strong><br>Small revisions are included as agreed; major scope changes are handled via a change order.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Intellectual property</strong><br>Final paid deliverables are transferred to you (unless otherwise agreed).<br>Pre-existing tools/libraries remain property of their original owners.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Confidentiality</strong><br>Both sides agree to keep private business and technical information secure.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Security &amp; blockchain risk</strong><br>We follow best practices, but blockchain systems can still carry risk (bugs, exploits, third-party failures, market/network issues).</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Third-party dependencies</strong><br>Wallets, RPC providers, cloud services, APIs, and chain infrastructure are outside direct control.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Warranty &amp; liability limits</strong><br>Services are typically provided with limited warranty; liability is capped as defined in the agreement.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Termination</strong><br>   Either party may terminate under agreed conditions; completed work/milestones remain billable.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Support &amp; maintenance</strong><br>   Post-launch support is covered only if included in contract or maintenance plan.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Dispute &amp; governing law</strong><br>   Any legal disputes follow the jurisdiction/law stated in the contract.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>If you want, I can also provide a <strong>client-facing full Terms of Service draft</strong> you can directly use on your website.</p>\nUser: what is ai based project of builderz\nAssistant: <p>Great question 👌</p>\n<p>At Builderz, an <strong>AI-based project</strong> usually means products where we combine <strong>AI + Web3</strong>, for example:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>AI-powered trading/analytics dashboards</strong> for crypto data  </li>\n<li><strong>Smart assistants/chatbots</strong> integrated into dApps  </li>\n<li><strong>Fraud/risk detection models</strong> for on-chain activity  </li>\n<li><strong>Recommendation engines</strong> for NFT/GameFi/DeFi platforms  </li>\n<li><strong>Automation agents</strong> that interact with smart contracts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want, I can share a <strong>sample AI + blockchain project concept</strong> (with features + tech stack) in 1 minute.</p>\n\n[Current message - respond to this]\nUser: okay what is your contact information?"}],"timestamp":1772092557210}}
